{"tid":2374471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★央行整治拒收人民幣現金行為　中國人壽等16家機構受罰","createTime":"2021-01-21T08:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:49:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4cffc28933fbd6bee2ae72aecc7839f8843966f","tid":2374471,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"內地電子支付發展迅速，然而店家拒收現金問題亦開始浮現。自去年10月，人民銀行以服務消費、暢通支付流通環境、保障民生為目標導向，發布人民幣現金收付指引公告，加強規範引導，並深入開展拒收人民幣現金行為集中整治。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒今日（1月20日）報道，2020年四季度，人民銀行依法對16家拒收現金的單位及相關責任人作出經濟處罰，處罰金額從500元至50萬元人民幣不等，當中包括中國人壽。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/577471/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%B2%BB%E6%8B%92%E6%94%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E7%AD%8916%E5%AE%B6%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8F%97%E7%BD%B0?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=hk01&amp;itm_content=all&amp;itm_medium=web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F577471%2F%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%2595%25B4%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%2594%25B6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25BD%25E7%25AD%258916%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%25BD%25B0%3Fitm_source%3Duniversal_search%26itm_campaign%3Dhk01%26itm_content%3Dall%26itm_medium%3Dweb&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=70954c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/577471/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%B2%BB%E6%8B%92%E6%94%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%BD%E7%AD%8916%E5%AE%B6%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8F%97%E7%BD%B0?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=hk01&amp;itm_content=all&amp;itm_medium=web</a>"},{"pid":"ec2862606aab27272059af5e89fb79e20d95a7a1","tid":2374471,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"下階段，人民銀行將堅持宣傳引導與嚴肅懲治相結合，持續深入整治，暢通投訴舉報渠道，規範核查相關線索，對核實為拒收現金的行為依法處罰並予以曝光，切實保護消費者的合法權益。同時，廣大經營主體應強化法治觀念、維護人民幣法定地位，誠信經營、尊重公眾支付選擇權，提升服務、共同打造現金和諧流通環境"},{"pid":"c659f250a6fe187e25cbbec93b0b95edc5b16177","tid":2374471,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2173321/org/380312e9c630102637637cefc1c7d760.png/xUDWHvg2kftkht4gaXjc0LS2g_Upo9GJu_fOL7v3zi8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2173321%2Forg%2F380312e9c630102637637cefc1c7d760.png%2FxUDWHvg2kftkht4gaXjc0LS2g_Upo9GJu_fOL7v3zi8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=bef4c5c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d31a463d7ec7ff4f09420274a57e01ff5b0848be","tid":2374471,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"Make 偽鈔 Great Again"},{"pid":"8845f21416ea73d52cfd13bbd3385253772dd049","tid":2374471,"uid":81698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:13:22.000Z","msg":"偽鈔多到無人敢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866571979b24faa1a1cf93a672681989ce06200c","tid":2374471,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"梗係啦，大陸咁多假錢同埋D錢全部融融爛爛。"},{"pid":"39a2b858ec9c38151cd23564bb7dc67e58c5f158","tid":2374471,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"唔係想將人仔電子化咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc2ef9c597f83621a54117a9c62a230afb15427","tid":2374471,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a2b858ec9c38151cd23564bb7dc67e58c5f158","tid":2374471,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21